text.tspan: As customers what can we do?
If we search “chocolate bath challenge” on
youtube, more than 100 videos would show up and
the lastest was uploaded two weeks ago.
Say NO to Chocolate Bath Challenge
Be aware that different types of chocolate may
require special storing conditions. Since they
came a long way from cocoa farms to our homes,
don’t just let them wasted inside our
refrigerators.
Store Chocolate Better
Are they mixed in with ‘dirty’ cocoa? Are their
cocoa sources traceable on the website? There
are companies which have already taken actions
to slow down the wheel of deforestation, it’s
never too late for us to recognize and support
their efforts.
Pay attention to the cocoa sources
of your favorite chocolate brand
The least effort we can
contribute is to not waste any
chocolate (this is applicable
to other food too).
